==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Doubtless
<hw>Doubt"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Free from fear or
suspicion.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Pretty child, sleep <qex>doubtless</qex> and secure.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Doubtless</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Doubtless
<hw>Doubt"less</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Undoubtedly; without
doubt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Doubtlessly</ent>⟦br⟧
